name: BTP Korp
description:
An original design created for the Bring the Paint festival using the Fingers Korpworm and featuring the Blackworm motif in the corner. This was a hand drawn piece that was then digitised in Illustrator and Photoshop to create this artwork.

Korpworm is a recurring character that features in a lot of my work. Blackworm is a manifestation of mental illness the frequently appears in the background of my artwork.
